<tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><img border="0" src="../triangle.JPG"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="#004242"><b>HORNETS</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Group / Solo:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Solo - Necromancer</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Mob Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">33 to 43</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Burning Woods</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Location:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">-2500 +2500 (approximately)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Character Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">44 to 52</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Strategy:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">The Hornets surrounding this area come in three types; Ash Hornets, Cinder Hornets, and Ember Hornets.  Ash Hornets tend to be in the lower 30s and most will con green to PCs hunting here.  The Cinder Hornets are in the upper 30s and have 2k to 3k hps.  The Ember Hornets are in the low 40s and have up to 4k hps.  The last group is the Scoriae Hornets that have over 5k hps and are in the upper level 40s (these usually aren’t worth engaging if you aren’t over level 49).  If you enter the zone from Dreadlands, follow the nearby path until there is a flat clearing on your left, as it makes an ideal pulling-to spot.
<br><br>
The strategy to taking down the hornets is rather easy.  They have a low agro radius, don’t chase too fast, and if you are in trouble you can run far enough and they will discontinue following.  If you are level 49 or above, I recommend pulling with a lifetap, running to a safe place where you have your pet parked, send in your pet, darkness and then fear.  Cascading Darkness is nice because of the massive amount of damage that it will deal to the hornet, but Dooming Darkness will work just fine and the shorter cast and recast time is helpful.
<br><br>
Stay away from heat based damage spells including the heat blood series, Asystole, and Ignite Blood as they are resisted VERY often.  Because the mobs are fairly easy the pet can take care of them by itself if you keep them feared and snared. But try keeping lich form up and recasting Bond of Death when needed (or Call of Bones and multiple lifetaps if you aren’t level 49 yet).  This will help reduce overall downtime (which shouldn’t be too much to begin with).
<br><br>
The hornets should be numerous enough to keep you busy, even with a partner or two.  There are some other mobs that spawn nearby including Sarnaks, Wurms and Gorillas.  Be careful of the Wurms and the Sarnak Casters, as they are capable of wiping out those that are unprepared.
<br><br>
<b>Additional Information</b>
<br><br>
<i>Ash Hornets</i> - level 33 to 37 (around 1700 HPs)
<br><i>Cinder Hornets</i> - level 36 to 40 (around 2500 HPs)
<br><i>Ember Hornets</i> - level 39 to 43 (around 3700 HPs)
<br><i>Scoriae Hornets</i> - level 42 to 46 (around 5300 HPs)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">annick (The Tribunal)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>6.6</b> (average of <b>10</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this spot:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><FORM ACTION = "ratehg.asp" METHOD = post><SELECT NAME="Voting"><OPTION VALUE="0">Rate this Spot</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="1">1 - Don't even bother</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="2">2</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="3">3</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="4">4</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="5">5 - It is ok</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="6">6</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="7">7</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="8">8</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="9">9</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="10">10 - You must come here</OPTION></SELECT><INPUT TYPE = "hidden" NAME = "intHGID" VALUE = 127><INPUT TYPE = "submit" VALUE="Rate It!"></form></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing